---

## Code Review Checklist

- [ ] Type hints on all functions; async/await correct (no blocking in async)
- [ ] SQL schema-prefixed; FK via `.get() or None`
- [ ] SCD changes logged to `tag_history`; audit to `audit_core.log_entry`
- [ ] Tests for new tasks; docstrings on public functions
- [ ] `schema.sql` updated if DB changed (same commit)
- [ ] No secrets in code (`.env*`, `ssh/`, `logs/prod/` not read)
- [ ] If new tech → context7 consulted; if arch change → pgedge validated

